**Anything else relevant?**

Issue #36688 provided me with a workaround, I created my own LocationStrategy:

```TypeScript
import { Injectable } from '@angular/core';
import { HashLocationStrategy } from '@angular/common';

@Injectable()
export class PatchedHashLocationStrategy extends HashLocationStrategy {
	prepareExternalUrl(internal: string): string {
		return super.prepareExternalUrl(internal) + window.location.search;
	}
}
```

However issue #36688 required the query params to come before the fragments, I require the query params to be part of the fragment.

